{"tid":1273980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"無知一問，室內可唔可以用催淚彈","createTime":"2019-07-01T15:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T17:50:58.000Z","uid":201662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fe96de14d00f8c6d585606d58dd88df2469df0da","tid":1273980,"uid":201662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:20:46.000Z","msg":"如果班狗係立法會催淚彈咁所有義士都會中招走唔到，得班狗可以行動自如<br />\n<br />\n但同時立法會有好多記者，一用催淚彈就實傷到佢地，到時實被全世界唱<br />\n<br />\n如果真係清場，班狗係咪只可以用胡椒噴霧同警棍，因為用更同級嘅武力就一定會傷到記者<br />\n <br />\n最後義士小心，唔好被狗包抄，即使被包圍就所有人向同一個方向突破<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">天佑香港</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">天佑義士</div></span></span>"},{"pid":"b8da276c28ef62c385db409a58a9faa05f792517","tid":1273980,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:23:24.000Z","msg":"文宣幫傳<br />\n提防散水 <br />\n人少先危險<br />\n唔好信擇日再戰<br />\n全力支援現場決定<br />\n發夢香港人盡快出去支援準備反包圍<br />\n發夢需要各種補給<br />\n發夢需要照明燈<br />\n一定要頂住 堅持住！<br />\n香港要改變！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不撤不散<br />\n<br />\n一定要捉住今次機會<br />\n絕對唔好再浪費<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油！"},{"pid":"5fee77a4e3147a40a3bc377baab347690a14159c","tid":1273980,"uid":193072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:24:36.000Z","msg":"緊係可以"},{"pid":"ec2d7fffccb95d9be5dc338e5059e4ce146d35ae","tid":1273980,"uid":181318,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:27:04.000Z","msg":"可唔可以都會照用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7459c3987d6e3ca272d0f95bcefa51ebf66c000f","tid":1273980,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:33:39.000Z","msg":"可以 但好多外國記者"},{"pid":"25fdf3226311ab09223cc0b60ba4a5c37599c51f","tid":1273980,"uid":156771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T15:38:31.000Z","msg":"就算說明書寫唔俾。。但有意思？<br />\n布袋彈話只可以寫下半身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後呢？"},{"pid":"96aa93f698239fca33b4e1128f441f2b760ba766","tid":1273980,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:50:58.000Z","msg":"Launcher grenade 應該唔可以，普通裝備催淚水先適合，室內用催淚彈要特別設計一般for捉barricade咗嘅 armed suspect ，唔同一般室外用c crowd/riot control 款式<br />\n1. 室內擴散緩慢，HVAC唔係風向咁易掌握（但可以調節到），會積聚濃度過高，限制效用以至出現反效果（對雙方都係），甚至飄到其他位造成 collateral damage <br />\n2. 有機會火燭（睇邊種）<br />\n3. 清理困難<br />\n萬一用咗要 damage control 通風系統可以set抽出去，上次金鐘站就要研究下咩事<br />\nRubber bursting cs hand grenade (eg 俾人踢爆料嘅Chemring N225) 可以"}]}